value.title: Azure Friday | Profiling Live Azure Web Apps with Application Insights
value.excerpt: Dan Taylor joins Scott Hanselman to talk about being able to get a code-level analysis of slow requests in production using the Application Insights profiler for Azure App Service. Dan shows Scott how to use the Application Insights Profiler to quickly get to the bottom of two different performance issues
